    <item>
      <title>Arththi prabandham</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/kAvyam/drAviDam/vara-vara-saumya-sundara-jAmAtR-muniH/arthi-prabandhaH/sarva-prastutiH/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vishvAsa.github.io/rAmAnujIyam/kAvyam/drAviDam/vara-vara-saumya-sundara-jAmAtR-muniH/arthi-prabandhaH/sarva-prastutiH/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Source: &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/index.php/2016/05/arththi-prabandham/&#34;&gt;TW&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;SrI: SrImathE SatakOpAya nama: SrImathE rAmAnujAya nama: SrImath varavaramunayE nama:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/ramanuja-srirangam.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/ramanuja-srirangam.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/ramanuja-srirangam.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;ramanuja-srirangam&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/emperumanar/&#34;&gt;SrI rAmAnuja&lt;/a&gt; – SrIrangam&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/mamunigal-srirangam.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;figure class=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;a href=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/mamunigal-srirangam.jpg&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;img src=&#34;https://divyaprabandham.koyil.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/mamunigal-srirangam.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;mamunigal-srirangam&#34; title=&#34;&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &#xA;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/2012/09/23/azhagiya-manavala-mamunigal/&#34;&gt;maNavALa mAmunigaL&lt;/a&gt; – SrIrangam&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;e-book – &lt;a href=&#34;https://1drv.ms/b/s!AiNzc-LF3uwygxHn7aePCEH7LtpY&#34;&gt;https://1drv.ms/b/s!AiNzc-LF3uwygxHn7aePCEH7LtpY&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/2012/09/23/azhagiya-manavala-mamunigal/&#34;&gt;maNavALa mAmunigaL&lt;/a&gt; starts his most-celebrated literary contribution to our sath sampradhAyam with a beautiful samskritha prabandham named yathirAja vimSathi in glorification of &lt;a href=&#34;http://acharyas.koyil.org/index.php/emperumanar/&#34;&gt;SrI rAmAnuja&lt;/a&gt; while he was residing in &lt;a href=&#34;http://azhwarthirunagari.koyil.org/&#34;&gt;AzhwArthirunagari&lt;/a&gt; and performing kainkaryam at &lt;a href=&#34;http://bhavishyadhacharyan.koyil.org/&#34;&gt;bhavishyadhAchAryan sannidhi&lt;/a&gt;. This is a collection of heart-melting 20 SlOkas in samskritham revealing his total dependence on yathirAja (SrI rAmAnuja – who is the king of mendicants).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
